Our largest venue, this contemporary yet, regal space lives up to its name!

  • "Sycamore Room" just added!! A flex space has also been added as either a separate meeting space or pre-function space.
  • Magnificent exposed brick bookends the 6,000-square-ft space
  • Spectacular floor-to-ceiling palladium windows
  • Seats up to 300 guests with a dance floor
  • Cool and comfortable courtyard just outside
  • Attached atrium for guests to enjoy cocktails & hors doeuvres

Our largest wedding venue, this contemporary yet, regal space lives up to its name!

  • Expanded pre-function space offers greater flexibility for your event needs. Outfitted with sleek nano walls, this adaptable area can seamlessly transform into a private meeting space, a stylish cocktail lounge, or an extension of your main event, designed to flow effortlessly with your vision
  • Magnificent exposed brick bookends the 6,000-square-ft space
  • Spectacular floor-to-ceiling palladium windows
  • Seats up to 300 guests with a dance floor
  • Stunning outdoor courtyard arranged with ample tables and chairs, plush soft seating, and anchored by elegant brick fireplaces and a cozy fire pit, this space is perfect for cocktail hours, casual mingling, or simply enjoying the fresh air
